mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "As I See It, by Bob Osgood", "Lift and Use", "Calling Progressive Squares", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Ladies on the Square", "Callers Round-Up", "The Square Dancers Who Own an Island", "The Red Barn of Pueblo, Colo.", "The Marmons of Boise", "Overseas Square Dance Dateline in Pictures", "Style Series: Something Traditional-Lady Round Two, The Gents Fall Thru", "Round the Outside Ring", "SIO Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Herb Engender", "Paging the Roundancers: George and MIllie Ireland" and "Experimental Lab: Square Turn Thru".
